name: InsurancePlan
title: InsurancePlan
description: Details of a Health Insurance product/plan provided by an organization.

elements.name: InsurancePlan
elements.description: Details of a Health Insurance product/plan provided by an organization.

elements.name: identifier
elements.description: Business identifiers assigned to this health insurance plan which remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

elements.name: status
elements.description: The current state of the health insurance plan.

elements.name: type
elements.description: The kind of health insurance plan.

elements.name: name
elements.description: Official name of the health insurance plan.

elements.name: alias
elements.description: A list of alternate names that the product is known as, or was known as in the past.

elements.name: period
elements.description: The period of time that the health insurance plan is available.

elements.name: ownedBy
elements.description: The entity that is providing the health insurance plan.

elements.name: administeredBy
elements.description: An organization which administer other services such as underwriting, customer service and/or claims processing on behalf of the health insurance plan's ownedBy.

elements.name: coverageArea
elements.description: The geographic region in which a health insurance plan's benefits apply.

elements.name: contact
elements.description: The contact for the health insurance plan.

elements.name: endpoint
elements.description: The technical endpoints providing access to services operated for the health insurance plan.

elements.name: network
elements.description: Reference to the network included in the health insurance plan.

elements.name: coverage
elements.description: Details about the coverage offered by the insurance product.
